creator: abdLearn
descriptionHtml:
The application calculates if the means of the sample groups have the same means or at least one is different by contrasting hypotheses using the analysis of variance. Statistical data that is entered is stored in cells.
The calculation is made by entering statistical data such as the level of significance, the total samples that will be in each group, then fill in the statistical data in each cell. The results can be exported in PDF.
Linear regression is calculated by entering statistical data such as the level of confidence, and the data of the independent and dependent variable.
The calculation of distributions such as Fisher, Normal and Tstudent is carried out using statistical data, the level of significance, the degrees of freedom of the numerator and denominator.
descriptionShort: Calculation of analysis of variance Linear regression and distributions

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:

Customizable design with dark background.
